t-rem13px leading-rem20px mt-rem12px">The menstrual cycle is a sequence of =
events that occurs as your body prepares for pregnancy each month.</figcapt=
ion></figure><div data-identity=3D"rich-text" class=3D""><h3 data-identity=
=3D"headline" class=3D"text-gray-900 font-bold leading-rem30px text-rem25px=
 bp600:text-rem32px bp600:leading-rem38px mt-rem32px mb-rem16px break-words=
  ">What is menstruation?</h3><p data-identity=3D"paragraph-element" class=
=3D"text-gray-800 my-rem16px text-rem19px leading-rem34px  ">Menstruation i=
s the monthly shedding of the lining of your uterus. Menstruation is also k=
nown by the terms menses, menstrual period, menstrual cycle or period. Mens=
trual blood =E2=80=94 which is partly blood and partly tissue from the insi=
de of your <a data-identity=3D"link" href=3D"https://my.clevelandclinic.org=
/health/body/22467-uterus" target=3D"_blank" class=3D"text-brandBlue-500 un=
derline underline-offset-[5px] decoration-1 break-words hover:text-blue-800=
 transition">uterus</a> =E2=80=94 flows from your uterus through your <a da=
ta-identity=3D"link" href=3D"https://my.clevelandclinic.org/health/body/232=
79-cervix" target=3D"_blank" class=3D"text-brandBlue-500 underline underlin=
e-offset-[5px] decoration-1 break-words hover:text-blue-800 transition">cer=
vix</a> and out of your body through your <a data-identity=3D"link" href=3D=
"https://my.clevelandclinic.org/health/body/22469-vagina" target=3D"_blank"=
 class=3D"text-brandBlue-500 underline underline-offset-[5px] decoration-1 =
break-words hover:text-blue-800 transition">vagina</a>.</p><div data-identi=
ty=3D"billboard-ad" class=3D"flex bp1100:hidden print:hidden max-w-[400px] =
